{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"想念毛主席——苗族民歌","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":10,"day":14}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"想念毛主席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——苗族民歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在以前的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们年纪还小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的只一岁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的是二岁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席长征经过我们的地方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写下字在寨边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在苗家觉醒起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能有吃有穿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后来我们稍长大了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈告诉我们："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你们要知道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以前有一个我们的救星经过这里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是只见他去了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不见他再来啦！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们等了又等，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等了十四年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十五年到了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的父亲——救星来到了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来叫我们起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们就聚集在一起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟着我们的毛主席走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们有吃有穿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变得白胖胖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像泉水一般的清清爽爽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像珠子一样的圆亮亮。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}